      "content": "i know u aren't a doctor but i just need to know if the math makes sense. if i take 400mg every 2 hours, i would be taking a lot but it keeps the level in my blood steady so the pain doesnt spike again. isnt that how most pain meds work? like staying ahead of the inflammation?",
